OL,3,CIs this the most potholed street in
OL,4,Cthe UK?
OL,6,FA road that has been covered in almost
OL,7,F100 potholes and renown for being the
OL,8,Fworst in the Midlands has been
OL,9,Fpartially resurfaced.
OL,11,FBirches Park Road in Codsall in
OL,12,FWolverhampton is being repaired by
OL,13,FStaffordshire County Council after it
OL,14,Fannounced it was investing an
OL,15,Fadditional #8million into fixing
OL,16,Fpotholes.
