OL,3,CIs this the most potholed street in
OL,4,Cthe UK?
OL,6,FCllr Mark Deaville said: "We've
OL,7,Frepaired 20,000 additional potholes
OL,8,Fthis year and the investment has also
OL,9,Fenabled us to deploy eight additional
OL,10,Fcrews, and they are working right
OL,11,Facross the county.
OL,13,F"Potholes are basically created by
OL,14,Fwater, and flooding issues deteriorate
OL,15,Fthe road, so this August and
OL,16,FSeptember, we cleared 8,000 gullies,
OL,17,Fcompared to 4,000 last year."
OL,19,FITV News Central reported on the
OL,20,Froad's potholes in August this year.
