OL,3,CIs this the most potholed street in
OL,4,Cthe UK?
OL,6,FThe potholes are being repaired, and
OL,7,Fsections are being re-tarmacked, but
OL,8,Fthe council is not resurfacing the
OL,9,Fentire road.
OL,11,FGary Pritchard, who has lived on the
OL,12,Froad for 23 years, said: "It's good
OL,13,Fit's being done, thanks to Central
OL,14,FNews mostly I think, but I still think
OL,15,Fthey should have took the road up.
OL,17,F"For 300 yards, I just don't see the
OL,18,Fpoint.
