OL,6,F"They'll be back again next March or
OL,7,FApril because it will be dug up again,
OL,8,Fso it's good something's being done
OL,9,Fbut I do think they could have done
OL,10,Fthe (whole) road."
OL,12,FWork on the road should be completed
OL,13,Fwithin three days.
